{
  "_comment_": [
    "DO NOT commit a populated .mcp.json — paths are absolute per user machine.",
    "",
    "To regenerate .mcp.json after cloning this repo:",
    "  Option A (recommended): clone init-project + run adopt:",
    "    git clone https://github.com/dipgle/init-project ~/Documents/projects/AI/init-project",
    "    ~/Documents/projects/AI/init-project/startup.sh .  # this writes .mcp.json",
    "  Option B: copy this template + replace <PROJECT_ABS_PATH> and <INIT_PROJECT_ABS_PATH>.",
    "",
    "Without .mcp.json the orchestrator still runs — MCP project-agent is only used by",
    "AI assistants (Claude Code / Cursor / Cline) for context briefing and devlog calls."
  ],
  "mcpServers": {
    "project-agent": {
      "type": "stdio",
      "command": "<INIT_PROJECT_ABS_PATH>/mcp/project-agent-rs/target/release/project-agent",
      "args": [],
      "env": {
        "PROJECT_MEMORY_DIR": "<PROJECT_ABS_PATH>/memory",
        "PROJECT_LOG_DIR": "<PROJECT_ABS_PATH>/logs"
      }
    }
  }
}
